biotools.summary: Fingerprint Analysis with Missing Data is an easy-to-use general-purpose program for dominant fingerprint data handling and analysis with a graphical user interface, supporting flexible data input and export to a variety of formats. Analysis capabilities include distance-based analysis, bootstrapping and consensus tree generation, allele frequency estimation, AMOVA, inter-population distances, Shannon’s index.
